\id LAM Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h RHAENGSAE LUNG 
\toc1 RHAENGSAE 
\toc2 Rhaengsae 
\toc3 Rhg 
\mt1 RHAENGSAE LUNG  
\mt2 (The Lamentations of Jeremiah)  
\is1 Introduction  
\im Rhaengsae lung dongah he 586 \sc b.c\sc*, Jerusalem bawkim a poci vaengah kosi a dung hlang la rhahnah la om. He hlohlai lung loh pocinah kawng bueng thui pawt tih, khopuei khopong kah khoponah te boeih a thui. Khopuei balaetih a poci ti kawng neh Pathen taengah rhennah a bih. Khopuei a a cungkunah kawng neh Jerusalem pilnam a cului kawng khaw a rhaengsae. A lung thumnah dongah tah khothae dung la ngai-uepnah a tlap. Pathen tah rhennah neh lungnah Boeipa, Pathen kah thinphatnah loh patang a bawt sak kawng a thui. A pali dongah ah rhihnah, sundaehnah, tlayaenah neh tawnbanah kawng a sak. A hnukkhueng ah tah Jerusalem pilnam ham rhennah bih tih thaduengthai sai sak ham a bih.  
\iot Oltlueng Rhoek  
\io1 Jerusalem ham omdam laa \ior 1. 1-21\ior*  
\io1 Boeipa khaw Rhal la om \ior 2. 1-21\ior*  
\io1 Ngaiuepnah om pueng \ior 3. 1-66\ior*  
\io1 Jerusalem Dantatnah \ior 4. 1-21\ior*  
\io1 Rhennah ham Thangthuinah \ior 5. 1-20\ior*  
